{
  "body": "```$proc.print: ‘foo’; $proc.close-stdin``` is wrong because .print is asynchronous. It should be ```whenever $proc.print: ‘foo’ { $proc.close-stdin }```.\r\n\r\nSee [RT #131764](https://rt.perl.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=131764).",
